annonstext:
We are looking for skilled and driven .NET Developers that want to be part of the journey to build up the new IT consultancy company of our customer from the foundation. We are looking for individuals that share with the passion for change and new possibilities in a friendly and positive environment. Our customer wants to create a culture based on professionalism, agility and passion for software development.

You have a burning desire for programming and are not afraid of learning new modern technologies and concepts. You are solution oriented and are not pleased with making something “work” but want to get a deeper understanding.

You are motivated of getting own responsibilities and the freedom of making own decisions. We are looking for persons with the right ambition and a strong inner drive. Finally, you are a team player and enjoys sharing your knowledge as well as obtaining knowledge from other skilled colleagues.

If you share our customers values and want to join their exciting journey from the beginning this can be the right place for you. To be part of our customer from the beginning will be rewarding.

If you find our proposal interesting and you meet the above requirements for the position, please don't hesitate to apply. We can assist with practical issues related to a relocation.

All applications are treated strictly confidential. Applications will be handled as they are received.

About Jobshark:

Jobshark is offering recruiting services for the IT sector. We have about 200 customers and among them some of Sweden's most prominent technology companies. Jobshark is headquartered in Sweden and is part of a company group with about 50 employees.
